Package edu.usfca.cs

Class Library

java.lang.Object
edu.usfca.cs.Entity
edu.usfca.cs.Library
public class Library extends Entity
Library is the class to create Library object Extends the Entity class contains array list of Songs, Artists and Albums as objects writeXML method: writes the playlist content to an XML file writeJSON method: writes the playlist content to a JSON file

Since:
1.0
Author:
Gizem Hazal Senturk
